s'en est-on pris à eux ?

244
00:12:37,130 --> 00:12:40,630
Panneau : "5 Membres" "Hass & Arcadia (Provisoire)" "Yamato" "Namiko" "Hass" "Akane" "Rikka"

245
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:40,610
